      <title>阿达尼集团与中东支持者 IHC 组建人工智能合资企业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/adani-group-forges-ai-joint-venture-with-middle-east-backer-ihc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由高塔姆·阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 领导的阿达尼集团 (Adani Group) 已与阿联酋国​​际控股公司 (UAE International Holding Co.) 的一个部门组建了一家合资企业，以探索人工智能和其他技术，这标志着这家印度企业集团与其中东支持者之间的联系不断加深。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/adani-group-forges-ai-joint-venture-with-middle-east-backer-ihc</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 08:49:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>小米推出首款电动汽车，志向成为中国的保时捷或特斯拉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/xiaomi-launches-first-su7-ev-with-ambition-to-be-china-s-porsche-or-tesla</link>
      <description><![CDATA[小米公司的亿万富翁联合创始人周四推出了该公司的首款电动汽车，宣称其雄心勃勃的目标是在 15 至 20 年内成为全球顶级汽车制造商，并与特斯拉公司和保时捷公司竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/xiaomi-launches-first-su7-ev-with-ambition-to-be-china-s-porsche-or-tesla</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 07:18:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本将于二月第三次尝试发射 H3 火箭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/japan-to-make-third-attempt-at-launching-h3-rocket-in-february</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本计划在 2 月发射其旗舰 H3 火箭，此前日本在 2023 年因代价高昂的失误和重大挫折而两次尝试发射该飞船均以失败告终。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/japan-to-make-third-attempt-at-launching-h3-rocket-in-february</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 02:02:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球需求回升，韩国芯片产量猛增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/south-korea-chip-output-jumps-in-sign-of-returning-global-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国半导体行业的产量和出货量均创下多年来的最大增幅，突显了技术势头的复苏，这对该国明年的经济前景和全球科技行业来说是个好兆头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/south-korea-chip-output-jumps-in-sign-of-returning-global-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 01:32:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管中国消费剧烈波动，京东仍准备大幅加薪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/jd-com-preps-big-pay-hikes-even-as-chinese-consumption-gyrates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[京东计划明年大幅提高员工工资，这对于一家在 2024 年面临激烈竞争和不确定的中国消费的电子商务公司来说是一项重大举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/jd-com-preps-big-pay-hikes-even-as-chinese-consumption-gyrates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 01:24:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Apple Watch 销售禁令被搁置</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-27/apple-watch-sales-ban-put-on-hold-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司赢得了一项法庭裁决，暂时中止了美国对其最新智能手表的销售禁令。在苹果寻求美国国际贸易委员会推迟裁决后，华盛顿一家上诉法院发布了临时中止令，该委员会阻止了 Apple Watch Series 9 和 Ultra 2 的进口和销售。Mark Gurman 报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-27/apple-watch-sales-ban-put-on-hold-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 19:10:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
